name: The Lady Mascott - Serenity Gate
description:
2.30

They asked me,​ how does it feels like?

You think how possibly you can understand how does it feels like.

It is like all colors depleted through your world.​ Roses leave their colors.
Sky is always grey. Raining through beautiful sunny day.

You are crying, as you smile.
Your thoughts are in vain as those dry tears on the back of your head.

It is like having a blackhole that hugs you, and you do deeper without coming back, say it is better to stay this way.

You feel the need to sleep forever.
You see fine, but doomed to be emotionally blind.
